`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The schedule system follows the same pattern as other pure systems in this codebase: pure query/computation functions + a thin stateful layer (module-level Map) for tracking last-triggered state per entity. The key insight is tracking which schedule _slot_ (by its `hour` field) was last triggered per NPC, so movement is initiated only on slot transitions — not on every tick.
